casebody.data:
Frank P. ROSSOTTO, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
WACHOVIA BANK, NATIONAL ASSOCIATION as Trustee, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3872 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 18, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed as from a nonfinal, nonappealable order. This dismissal is without prejudice to Appellant to challenge the trial court's denial of his motion for continuance in appeal 2D18-3922, which reviews the September 21, 2018, final judgment of foreclosure.

KHOUZAM, MORRIS, and ATKINSON, JJ., Concur.
